id=post-2 class="post-2 page type-page status-publish hentry"><header
class=entry-header><h1 class="entry-title">Home</h1></header><div
class=entry-content><h1 class="wp-block-heading">Welcome to Clandon Wood</h1><p>Come to see multiple award winning Clandon Wood for yourself – whether you are thinking about choosing a plot or just to visit our nature reserve you will always be welcome</p><h4 class="wp-block-heading">Our address</h4><p>Clandon Wood, Epsom Road, West Clandon, Guildford, Surrey GU4 7FN<br>(For older Sat Navs use GU4 7TT)<br>Our cemetery is located on the A246 close to the junction with the A25, is within easy reach of London and has close links to the A3 and M25.</p></div></article></div></div><div
id=homewidget1 class=widget-area><aside
